Snake Pit?

653
00:56:31,422 --> 00:56:33,257
(SIRINE MERAUNG DI KEJAUHAN)

654
00:56:48,238 --> 00:56:51,041
(DALAM BAHASA MANDARIN)
Tidak ada jalan keluar.

655
00:56:51,075 --> 00:56:52,977
